  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Fundacion DEHVI supports Costa Rican children under 5 years of age living in poverty and in high risk communities. We offer them high-quality early education inspired by Reggio Emilia pedagogy, 4 nutritious meals a day, a safe and secure enviroment, and we help them nurture values &amp; develop life long-skills. We have 6  child centers where we provide this service for 5 days a week through extended hours.This provides the opportunity for their parents to find a job and break from the poverty cycle</narrative>
  </description>
